latestPosts.caption:
not pictured:
the YEARS of hustle.
the early mornings, late nights. 
doubting ourselves. 
questioning why we signed up to work in such a difficult industry. 
seeing people raise more $$ than us & feeling like failures. 
then seeing those same companies fail & realizing that our discipline & work ethic is our secret weapon. 
we fought the odds, together. 
we pushed past our limits, together. 
and we became stronger, together. 

& we suck at celebrating our wins bc we’re always so “ok on to the next” 

so we’re posting this to savor this. 
with you. 

bc you’re a part of our story and we’re endlessly grateful ✨ 

Ok! see you at Whole Foods! 💚

latestPosts.caption:
WE’RE NOW IN WHOLE FOODS!! 🍫

Our Protein Brownies just landed in Whole Foods Market Southern Pacific! (Select California, Nevada, Arizona & Hawaii stores!)

Fun fact: we would buy ingredients for our at-home prototypes at Whole Foods so it’s a full circle moment to now have our products sold here! 

If you’re local, we’d love your help spreading the word: share this post, tell a friend, or shout it from the rooftops!

You can find us in the protein bar aisle 💪

Note: some stores are still stocking our brownies, so if you don’t see them on the shelves, it’d mean a lot if you kindly asked a manager to bring out Elavi’s protein brownies from the back 🙏🏼
